msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:129
msgid ""
"All element-wise operations (``+``, ``-``, ``*``, ``/``, ``**``, "
"comparisons, unary ``-``, ``abs``, and numpy ufuncs) operate on the scalar "
"constant value without allocating a full array:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:133
msgid "**Constant + constant** returns a new ``VTKConstantArray``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:134
msgid ""
"**Constant + regular array** substitutes the scalar and returns a "
"``VTKAOSArray`` with metadata (dataset, association) propagated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:137
msgid ""
"Reductions (``sum``, ``mean``, ``min``, ``max``, ``std``, ``var``, ``prod``, "
"``any``, ``all``) are computed in O(1) from the constant value and array "
"shape."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:141
msgid ""
"NumPy Integration/home/runner/work/vtk-docs-l10n/vtk-docs-l10n/out/repo/"
