#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:156
msgid ""
"Scalar indexing returns the constant value.  Slices and fancy indexing "
"return a new ``VTKConstantArray`` of the appropriate shape, still using O(1) "
"memory.  The array is read-only; ``__setitem__`` raises ``TypeError``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_constant_array.py:161
msgid ""
"Dataset Integration/home/runner/work/vtk-docs-l10n/vtk-docs-l10n/out/repo/"
